{"tid":862580,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[業主又贏]有研究指124幢工廈適合改裝成過渡性房屋 料十年可提供1萬8千個單位","createTime":"2018-10-15T02:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T04:19:54.000Z","uid":57424,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"98acc1dcedf2b60c39d6c2c39eceae9466e80a56","tid":862580,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T02:40:37.000Z","msg":"施政報告提出改裝整幢工廈作過渡性房屋，有團體研究指有124幢市區工廈適合改裝，估計10年可提供約1萬8千個單位，每幢造價介乎5千萬至2億元。<br />\n團體建議政府資助業主，否則很難吸引業主參與。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/174055440191018/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F174055440191018%2F&d=Pu874G7vRu0OUCz98EcujdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=205c8f38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/174055440191018/</a><br />\n<br />\n改裝都要政府資助比佢搵錢<br />\n依家口講話 5K月租 4人單位, 如果係咁申請條 1G上網, 玩下filecoin, 除時夠交租"},{"pid":"9f3923cff98f46a0869d7cc5cdc50bae8195d17c","tid":862580,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T02:41:46.000Z","msg":"劏房波又贏"},{"pid":"19ed963d75340f5ae8d6265130620f6db2728ab8","tid":862580,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f3923cff98f46a0869d7cc5cdc50bae8195d17c","tid":862580,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T02:41:46.000Z","msg":"劏房波又贏"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T02:46:15.000Z","msg":"條仆街除左做劏房生意其他都唔識"},{"pid":"09b86c7e0ba397b55df78f673f628427b7425cb7","tid":862580,"uid":2442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T02:50:21.000Z","msg":"改完之後，每間房一百尺，8千蚊租。"},{"pid":"4634e2863a72741d965cba14270b7ede263addae","tid":862580,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T02:54:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b573cd01a15b84a38bba67039e377d8775b1705","tid":862580,"uid":40397,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T03:19:48.000Z","msg":"有政府參與做